This is a brand page for the EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC trademark by Imperial Holdings, Inc. 
                                in Boca Raton, FL, 33486.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Imperial Holdings, Inc. of the EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC trademark.
                           






On Friday, March 27, 2015,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC by 
                        Imperial Holdings, Inc., Boca Raton, FL  33486.
                        The USPTO has given the EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC 
                        trademark serial  number of  86579521.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC is 
                        
                        
                                            NORM J. RICH of 
                                            Foley & Lardner Llp,  3000 K St NW Fl 6, Washington, DC 20007-5109 
                                .
                            The EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for EMERGENT CAPITAL, INC 
                            is Financial services in the nature of providing life settlement services, namely, the buying and selling of life insurance policies on the secondary and tertiary markets. 
                            





