MembershipsEmergent Capital is an active member of key U.S. and European life settlement trade associations.



The Life Insurance Settlement Association (LISA), headquartered in Orlando, is the oldest and largest organization in the life settlement market. The association’s mission is to advance the highest standards of practice and professional development for the industry.






The European Life Settlement Association (ELSA), based in London, is dedicated to the promotion of best practice and the positive development of the European life settlement industry’s reputation amongst all stakeholders. Emergent Capital’s in-house counsel, Michael Altschuler, serves on ELSA’s regulatory committee.





