Emergent Capital Inc.


            
            Emergent Capital, Inc. is a finance company, which engages in the investment in life settlements. It purchases individual policies and portfolios of life insurance. The company was founded on December 15, 2006 and is headquartered in Boca Raton, FL.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


